  "@type": "Process",
  "critical": false,
  "description": "Solid-state joining via rotating tool (500-1500 RPM, 50-200 mm/min feed). Tool friction heats metal to plasticized state (70-90% of melting point) without melting. Joins unweldable aluminum alloys (2xxx, 7xxx series) and dissimilar metals (Al-to-steel, Al-to-Cu) without brittle intermetallics. Tool materials: H13 steel for aluminum, PCBN for steel.",
  "early_win": false,
